{"name":"Song Talents, Adv: Twinperform*","permission":{"default":0,"N1fw6b6C7kQcxuhL":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Once per day, the bard may perform two songs as a standard action, but the combined MP cost cannot exceed his caster level. The two songs must have the same casting time and if they have a target, the targets for the songs may be different.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Advanced Song Talent"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"special"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"twinperform","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Bard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"EMBSzTXm3gGr5aIU"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"5ILMZtuQshTBGayr"}
{"name":"Grant Move Action","permission":{"default":0,"N1fw6b6C7kQcxuhL":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 3rd level, a bard can direct and motivate his allies to act immediately. Once per day, as a move action, he may grant an extra move action to any or all of his allies within 30 feet (but not to himself). Each of the affected allies takes this extra move action immediately, acting in their current initiative order. This extra action does not affect the allies&rsquo; initiative count; the round continues normally after the bard&rsquo;s turn is over. (This may mean, for example, that an ally whose initiative count immediately follows the bard&rsquo;s may get an extra move action from the bard, followed directly by a full round worth of actions on the ally&rsquo;s turn.)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>At 6th level and every three bard levels thereafter, a bard gains the ability to grant an extra move action to his allies <span lang=\"en-US\">an additional time</span> per day. A character can take only one extra move action per round. (In other words, two bards can&rsquo;t use this ability on the same ally in the same round.) If an ally chooses not to take the extra move action, it is lost.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"move"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"30","units":"ft","maxIncrements":"1","minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"floor(@classes.bard.lvl/3)"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"labe