{"name":"Song Talents: Bardic Inspiration","permission":{"default":0,"N1fw6b6C7kQcxuhL":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>The bard can inspire others through stirring words or music. To do so, he uses a swift action on his turn to choose one creature other than himself within 60 feet of him who can hear him. That creature gains one Bardic Inspiration die, a d6. Once within the next 10 minutes, the creature can roll the die and add the number rolled to one ability check, attack roll, or saving throw it makes. The creature can wait until after it rolls the d20 before deciding to use the Bardic Inspiration die, but must decide before the GM says whether the roll succeeds or fails. Once the Bardic Inspiration die is rolled, it is lost. A creature can have only one Bardic Inspiration die at a time. The bard can use this feature a number of times per day equal to his Charisma modifier (a minimum of once). His Bardic Inspiration die changes when he reaches certain levels in this class. The die becomes a d8 at 5th level, a d10 at 10th level, and a d12 at 15th level.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Song Talent"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"swift"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"@abilities.cha.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"bardicInspiration","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Bard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"85505NZQkMCzXBzV"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"9OstFT4GJWxDANgG"}
{"_id":"9tC3d5WM5CjwQtii","name":"Bard","permission":{"default":0,"N1fw6b6C7kQcxuhL":3},"type":"class","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A bright tune to soothe a party&rsquo;s wounds&hellip; A brisk march to raise a party&rsquo;s spirits&hellip; A forbidden chant to weaken a party&rsquo;s foes&hellip; Bards use music as their weapon. A bard is the quintessential entertainer, blessed with musical skills that are the envy of all others. Their songs and inspirations often protect their allies from harm, heal wounds, and inspired them to do great things. Untold wonders and secrets exist for those skillful enough to discover them. Through cleverness, talent, and magic, these cunning few unravel the wiles of the world, becoming adept in the arts of persuasion, manipulation, and inspiration.</p>\n<p>Role:&nbsp;Bards capably confuse and confound their foes while inspiring their allies to ever-<wbr />greater daring. While accomplished with both weapons and magic, the true strength of bards lies outside melee, where they can support their companions and undermine their foes without fear of interruptions to their performances.</p>\n<p>Alignment:&nbsp;Any</p>\n<p>Hit Die:&nbsp;d8</p>\n<p>Starting Wealth:&nbsp;3d6 &times; 10 gil (average 105 gil.) In addition, each character begins play with an outfit worth 10 gil or less.</p>\n<p>Class Skills<br />The bard&rsquo;s class skills (and the key ability for each skill) are Acrobatics (Dex), Appraise (Int), Bluff (Cha), Climb (Str), Craft (Int), Diplomacy (Cha), Disguise (Cha), Escape Artist (Dex), Intimidate (Cha), Knowledge (all) (Int), Linguistics (Int), Perception (Wis), Perform (Cha), Profession (Wis), Sense Motive (Wis), Sleight of Hand (Dex), Spellcraft (Int), Stealth (Dex), and Use Magic Device (Cha).</p>\n<p>Skill Points Per Level:&nbsp;6 + Int modifier</p>\n<p>Class Main Ability Scores:<br />The bard mainly focuses on DEX for martial combat and CHA for their class features and songs.</p>\n<h2 id=\"tablepress-11-name\">Table: Bard</h2>\n<table id=\"tablepress-11\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-11-name\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 10%;\">Level</th>\n<th>Special</th>\n<th style=\"width: 10%;\">Song Level</th>\n<th style=\"width: 10%;\">Minor Auras</th>\n<th style=\"width: 10%;\">Major Auras</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Type</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Bardic Performance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#musical-power\">Musical Power</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Countersong</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#jingles\">Jingles</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Distraction</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Fascinate</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Inspire Courage</a>&nbsp;+1,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#minor-auras\">Minor Aura</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#limit-breaks\">Limit Breaks</a></td>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#versatile-performance\">Versatile Performance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(1d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#well-versed\">Well-Versed</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#song-talents\">Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Inspire Competence</a>&nbsp;+2,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#grant-move-action\">Grant Move Action</a>&nbsp;(1/day)</td>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#major-auras\">Major Aura</a>&nbsp;+1,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#dissonance\">Dissonance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(2d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#song-talents\">Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a>&nbsp;I,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspire-courage\">Inspire Courage</a>&nbsp;+2,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#additional-song\">Additional Song</a></td>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#versatile-performance\">Versatile Performance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(3d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#grant-move-action\">Grant Move Action</a>&nbsp;(2/day),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#song-talents\">Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#skilled-performer\">Skilled Performer</a>&nbsp;+5,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspire-competence\">Inspire Competence</a>&nbsp;+3</td>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#major-auras\">Major Aura</a>&nbsp;+2,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(4d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#song-talents\">Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Inspire Greatness</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#grant-move-action\">Grant Move Action</a>&nbsp;(3/day)</td>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a>&nbsp;II,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#additional-song\">Additional Song</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#versatile-performance\">Versatile Performance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(5d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#song-talents\">Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Inspire Competence</a>&nbsp;+4,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspire-courage\">Inspire Courage</a>&nbsp;+3</td>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#major-auras\">Major Aura</a>&nbsp;+3,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#soothing-performance\">Soothing Performance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(6d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#grant-move-action\">Grant Move Action</a>&nbsp;(4/day),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#advanced-song-talents\">Advanced Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#skilled-performer\">Skilled Performer</a>&nbsp;+10,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#can't-stop-my-performance\">Can't Stop My Performance</a></td>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance%3C/a%3E%20(7d6),%20%3Ca%20href=\">Frightening Tune</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#versatile-performance\">Versatile Performance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#advanced-song-talents\">Advanced Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>15th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a>&nbsp;III,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspire-competence\">Inspire Competence</a>&nbsp;+5,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspire-heroics\">Inspire Heroics</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#grant-move-action\">Grant Move Action</a>&nbsp;(5/day)</td>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>16th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#major-auras\">Major Aura</a>&nbsp;+4,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(8d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#advanced-song-talents\">Advanced Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Inspire Courage</a>&nbsp;+4 ,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#unstoppable-performance\">Unstoppable Performance</a></td>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>18th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#versatile-performance\">Versatile Performance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Funeral Ballad</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(9d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#grant-move-action\">Grant Move Action</a>&nbsp;(6/day),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#advanced-song-talents\">Advanced Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>19th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#skilled-performer\">Skilled Performer</a>&nbsp;+15,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/bardic-performance\">Inspire Competence</a>&nbsp;+6</td>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>20th</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a>&nbsp;IV,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#additional-song\">Additional Song</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#major-auras\">Major Aura</a>&nbsp;+5,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#bardic-performance\">Deadly Performance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#deadly-performance\">Master Bard</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#inspiration\">Inspiration</a>&nbsp;(10d6),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/bard/#advanced-song-talents\">Advanced Song Talents</a></td>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>Favored Class Bonuses</h2>\n<p>Instead of receiving an additional skill rank or hit point whenever they gain a level in a favored class, some races have the option of choosing from a number of other bonuses, depending upon their favored classes. The following options are available to the listed race who have bard as their favored class, and unless otherwise stated, the bonus applies each time you select the listed favored class reward.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/burmecian/\">Burmecian</a>:&nbsp;Increase the bonus provided by the bard&rsquo;s inspire competence performance by 1/6, and add 1/6 to the number of allies the bard can affect with his inspire greatness performance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/dwarf/\">Dwarf</a>:&nbsp;Reduce spell failure chance for performing bard songs when wearing medium armor by +1%. Once the total reaches 10%, the bard also receives Medium Armor Proficiency, if he does not already possess it.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/elvaan/\">Elvaan</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s CMD when resisting a disarm or sunder attempt.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/galka/\">Galka</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s total number of bardic performance rounds per day.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/gria/\">Gria</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s CMD when resisting a disarm or sunder attempt.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/half-breed/\">Half-Breed</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s total number of bardic performance rounds per day.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/hume/\">Hume</a>:&nbsp;Add one song from the bard song list to the bard&rsquo;s songbook. This song must be at least one level below the highest song level he can perform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/hypello/\">Hypello</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/6 to the DC of all songs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/beastman-tribes/lamia/\">Lamia</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s total number of bardic performance rounds per day.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/mithra/\">Mithra</a>:&nbsp;Add a +1/2 bonus on Bluff checks to lie and a +1/2 bonus on Diplomacy checks to gather information.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/moogle/\">Moogle</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/6 to the bonus provided by the bard&rsquo;s inspire courage bardic performance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/beastman-tribes/namazu/\">Namazu</a>:&nbsp;Treat the bard&rsquo;s level as +1/2 level higher for the purpose of determining the effect of the fascinate bardic performance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/beastman-tribes/sylph/\">Sylph</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s total number of bardic performance rounds per day.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/tarutaru/\">Tarutaru</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s total number of bardic performance rounds per day.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/varg/\">Varg</a>:&nbsp;Add +1/6 to the bonus provided by the bard&rsquo;s inspire courage bardic performance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/viera/\">Viera</a>:&nbsp;Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s CMD when resisting a disarm or sunder attempt.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/beastman-tribes/yagudo/\">Yagudo</a>: Add +1 to the bard&rsquo;s CMD when resisting a disarm or sunder attempt.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"id":"clff20-content.clff20-class-pack-bard.cNKS3SQQGOnrO6f7","dataType":"compendium","name":"Limit Break: Auric Beauty","img":"systems/clff20/icons/FFxiv%20icons/FFXIVIcons%20MainCommand%20(Others)/02_General/limit_break.png","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":0},{"id":"clff20-content.clff20-class-pack-bard.2EQuguzNMlSw1avL","dataType":"compendium","name":"Limit Break: Soul Voice","img":"systems/clff20/icons/FFxiv%20icons/FFXIVIcons%20MainCommand%20(Others)/02_General/limit_break.png","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":1},{"id":"clff20-content.clff20-class-pack-bard.bUUfdovSUiS7UdJS","dataType":"compendium","name":"Songs/Jingles","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":2},{"id":"clff20-content.clff20-class-pack-bard.yhKpWdqx7OKMqF2s","dataType":"compendium","name":"Musical Power","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":3},{"id":"clff20-content.clff20-class-pack-bard.RQp5cRyqEK0qeuDo","dataType":"compendium","name":"Auras","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":4},{"id":"clff20-content.clff20-class-pack-bard.wdtO30xitPjfF03S","dataType":"compendium","name":"Minor Aura","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":5},{"id":"clff20-content.clff20-class-pack-bard.1DiRRjonRq9V2XWa","dataType":"compendium","name":"Bardic Performance","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":6}