{"_id":"cNKS3SQQGOnrO6f7","name":"Limit Break: Auric Beauty","permission":{"default":0,"N1fw6b6C7kQcxuhL":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This Limit Break causes the bard to enhance his auras beyond their normal power. For a duration of 1 round + 1 round per four bard levels after 1st, the bard&rsquo;s auras have their radius increases by 15 feet (this is also doubled with <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/feats/class-feats/improved-aura/\">Improved Aura</a>) as well as allow the bard to project an additional minor or major aura at the same time as his current active auras, this additional aura does not count against his daily uses. The bard can maintain an additional minor or major aura at a time at 10th level and then at 20th level. This limit break requires only a swift action.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Limit Break"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"swift"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"1+(floor(([[@classes.bard.lvl]]-1) / 4))","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag"